column4: NSLOCTEXT("[D508678C40AE240674B5908DADF95E9F]", "E02E2CE74537AD5720A1A596CA9B8283", "If you want to go thru, you must accept my challenge.")
NSLOCTEXT("[D508678C40AE240674B5908DADF95E9F]", "7E29F46A42AD9A9D753F37BF6C8B03D3", "I let my guard down, but two on one isn\'t fair.")

column13: ((8, NSLOCTEXT("[D508678C40AE240674B5908DADF95E9F]", "0D499C3C434C366597A176BF4AB83399", "Well, that maybe so")),(9, NSLOCTEXT("[D508678C40AE240674B5908DADF95E9F]", "A8BAB5174C980408187D40804B82D07F", "Don\'t be a sore loser")))

column4: NSLOCTEXT("[D508678C40AE240674B5908DADF95E9F]", "380F6AE042384F9F7C0E29B472B01A91", "I never lose to anybody when it\'s a fair fight.")
NSLOCTEXT("[D508678C40AE240674B5908DADF95E9F]", "9F5721964413DB59ED6DA299B6A98BB6", "Let\'s fight one on one. Come back tomorrow at 04:00. Only Digimon will fight.")
NSLOCTEXT("[D508678C40AE240674B5908DADF95E9F]", "094918F045C15065A9202C990D3C8408", "It\'s a promise then. See you tomorrow!")
NSLOCTEXT("[D508678C40AE240674B5908DADF95E9F]", "097C9433480F3CD92D333FA993FE32CA", "You came back, good. Today, we\'ll fight fair!")
NSLOCTEXT("[D508678C40AE240674B5908DADF95E9F]", "F5A16F7444BE688E04B0B48303533A4B", "We\'re exploring and trying to save the island from danger.")
NSLOCTEXT("[D508678C40AE240674B5908DADF95E9F]", "6535A1F146FC0382F8D87FA470612F5E", "{Player} tries so hard to convince him!")
NSLOCTEXT("[D508678C40AE240674B5908DADF95E9F]", "22E8B60B424B1E7C9FB80590852A2B0C", "I\'ll help you. But, I\'ll have to see that city first.")
NSLOCTEXT("[D508678C40AE240674B5908DADF95E9F]", "4F5BCDD843EB43D8BB240F8E947D78EC", "You\'re late, but that gave me time to nurse my injury. Now let\'s go for it.")
